    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve truly babied it since day one! It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is flawless, the interior still has that fresh feel, and it\u2019s been perfectly maintained. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message and come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
