      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car has been pampered since day one and is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come by and see it for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
