      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six. This MA1.01 powerplant delivers 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring optimal damping and roll stiffness. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over ventilated, cross-drilled rotors with zero thermal fatigue. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented service history that confirms the integrity of the high-pressure fuel pump and cooling system. The underbody is exceptionally clean, with no signs of fluid seepage or bushing degradation. A rare, collector-grade specimen for the driver who demands mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
